data.description: Welcome to a wonderful and spacious townhome nested in a gated community.  This property offers: 4 Bedrooms, 3 Full Bathrooms, an office that could be used as a 5th bedroom, spacious and modern kitchen with solid granite countertops, Island and pantry, stainless steel appliances. Master bedroom has a nice walk-in closet. Master bathroom offers a dual sink vanity, Kitchen and Dinning on an open concept layout, washer and dryer are conveniently located on the third level. Two-car garage with ample space for your vehicles and additional storage options.  Centrally located in Concord, close to Shopping and Briones park.  Quick access to HWY 680.
